#

Aromatic Pork Tenderloin with Herb-infused Gravy and Creamy Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$25.99
680 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-proteindairy

Tags:

porkcomfort foodheartyfamily meal

Description

Succulent pork tenderloin drizzled with a rich herb gravy served alongside velvety garlic mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1.5 lbs
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh Rosemary: 1 tbsp, chopped
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tbsp, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Chicken Broth: 2 cups
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Potatoes: 2 lbs, peeled and cubed
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
